14
00:02:03,109 --> 00:02:08,009
Dia bahkan mulai merambat ke novel fantasi pahlawan

15
00:02:08,009 --> 00:02:10,409
dan mendapatkan penggemar wanita juga.

16
00:02:10,409 --> 00:02:12,409
Kau jelas tahu banyak tentang dia, Ayah.

17
00:02:12,409 --> 00:02:16,209
Tentu saja! Aku seorang detektif brilian.

18
00:02:18,009 --> 00:02:19,609
Ran.

19
00:02:20,909 --> 00:02:24,409
Horror Times Bulanan, Spesial Tentang Daisuke Torakura.

20
00:02:26,309 --> 00:02:28,309
Lembar jawaban, hah?

21
00:02:28,309 --> 00:02:29,609
Diam!

22
00:02:33,209 --> 00:02:35,009
Itu dia.

23
00:02:37,309 --> 00:02:40,009
Itu Puri Drakula?

